OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine conflict: BP under 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpressure to sell stake in  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FRussian firm               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Oil giant BP is under pressure from the
OL,6, UK government to offload its 20% stake 
OL,7, in the Russian state-owned oil firm    
OL,8, Rosneft, the BBC has been told.        
OL,10,FBusiness Secretary Kwasi Kwarteng spoke
OL,11,Fto BP boss Bernard Looney on Friday    
OL,12,Ffollowing Russia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,14,FHe "left Mr Looney in no doubt about   
OL,15,Fthe seriousness of government concerns 
OL,16,Fabout BP's overexposure to Russian     
OL,17,Finterests", an official said.          
OL,19,FBP has said it is "closely watching the
OL,20,Fconcerning developments" in Ukraine.   
